    <stitle>AIR COMPRESSOR: BENDIX TU-FLO 501 - CLEAN AND INSPECT - END COVER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="clean" graphiccount="0">
        <title>END COVER</title>
        <para>Check end covers for cracks and external damage. If main bearings are installed in the end cover, check
            for excessive wear and flat spots and replace them if required. The oil seals should be replaced using a
            press.
        </para>
